### 헬스체크
GET http://localhost:3000/

###

### 회원가입
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user1@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "nickname": "user1"
}

###

### 로그인
POST http://localhost:3000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user1@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

# 응답에서 accessToken 복사해서 아래 {{ACCESS_TOKEN}} 에 붙여넣기

###

### 내 정보 조회
GET http://localhost:3000/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
###

### 상품 등록
POST http://localhost:3000/products
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "멋진 상품",
  "description": "설명입니다",
  "price": 5000,
  "tags": ["태그1", "태그2"],
  "imageUrl": "https://via.placeholder.com/150"
}

###

### 전체 상품 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:3000/products

###

### 📦 특정 상품 조회 (ID=1 기준)
GET http://localhost:3000/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 상품 좋아요 (ID=1)
POST http://localhost:3000/products/1/like
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 상품 좋아요 취소 (ID=1)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/products/1/like
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 내가 좋아요한 상품 목록
GET http://localhost:3000/users/me/liked-products
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 게시글 등록
POST http://localhost:3000/articles
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "게시글 제목",
  "content": "게시글 내용입니다",
  "image": null
}

###

### 게시글 전체 목록
GET http://localhost:3000/articles

###

### 게시글 단건 조회 (ID=1 기준)
GET http://localhost:3000/articles/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 게시글 좋아요
POST http://localhost:3000/articles/1/like
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 게시글 좋아요 취소
DELETE http://localhost:3000/articles/1/like
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 내가 좋아요한 게시글 목록
GET http://localhost:3000/users/me/liked-articles
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 상품에 댓글 작성 (productId = 1 기준)
POST http://localhost:3000/products/1/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "이 상품 정말 좋아요!"
}

###

### 게시글에 댓글 작성 (articleId = 1 기준)
POST http://localhost:3000/articles/1/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "게시글 잘 봤어요 :)"
}

###

### 상품 댓글 목록 가져오기 (productId = 1 기준)
GET http://localhost:3000/products/1/comments

###

### 게시글 댓글 목록 가져오기 (articleId = 1 기준)
GET http://localhost:3000/articles/1/comments

###

### 댓글 수정 (commentId = 1 기준)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/comments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "수정된 댓글입니다!"
}

###

### 댓글 삭제 (commentId = 1 기준)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/comments/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### 댓글 내용이 빈 문자열
POST http://localhost:3000/articles/1/comments
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": ""
}

### 상품 등록 시 price에 문자열 전달
POST http://localhost:3000/products
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "잘못된 상품",
  "description": "price가 문자열임",
  "price": "abc",
  "tags": ["테스트"]
}